        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Expected behavior\r\n> The window separator for `/tmp/bar` should stay red, even after you move the window to the right with `<C-w>L`.\r\n\r\nBut that means the other window's border is overridden.\r\n\r\n> Can this issue be re-opened as a feature request, or is this considered a `wontfix`?\r\n\r\nWhat is the request? Perhaps this:\r\n\r\n- If 'winhighlight' is set on a window, its `WinSeparator` highlights _all_ borders.\r\n- If 'winhighlight' is set on multiple adjacent windows how is the priority decided?",
